{"tid":1682270,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"薄荷糖邊隻最勁薄荷, 提神","createTime":"2019-10-30T02:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:27:57.000Z","uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb00ac14a68f4923b928883dd5750c720c3f23ab","tid":1682270,"uid":321196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:55:44.000Z","msg":"試過HALLS荷氏的午夜風暴, AIRWAVES, 呢兩隻算係比較強, 已經比市面普遍強, 但食慣薄荷糖的食食下會覺得未最提神, 尤其整野整到倦倦地想提神時, 想搵隻強D<br />\n而所有漁夫之寶都食過, 原味同特強薄荷算當中最勁薄荷, 但效果其實比HALLS同AIRWAVES個人覺得都仲差少少<br />\n<br />\n有無人食過邊隻薄荷糖最勁薄荷, 又好提神"},{"pid":"808f452f4cc27256f32c0771733f26845ef0e2a2","tid":1682270,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:55:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人(眾籌到而家先35%, 仲要大家支持) <br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=7e1b061f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"b3b9959e7ac18a26102b0fb28b36c9664ff06cfe","tid":1682270,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"778371f9401ba215e56b8db34cb0d713ccdb37f3","tid":1682270,"uid":74852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"以前無印有出過隻無糖微辣黑薄荷<br />\n細細粒 勁過食一排爽浪<br />\n不過已經好耐都無見過"},{"pid":"b9c4fda730dd258ea86c2c4626c845c2a5bc51c1","tid":1682270,"uid":321196,"like":0,"di